playstore_details.title: Radiology Tutor
playstore_details.description:
*******PLEASE DON'T RATE DOWN WITHOUT COMMENTING WHY, OTHERWISE I CAN'T IMPROVE IT. READ BELOW TO SEE WHAT THE APP DOES, IF IT DOESN'T DO WHAT YOU WANT, YOU NEED A DIFFERENT APP*****
This is the app for Radiology Tutor - www.radiologytutor.com

Included are the following calculators:
Absolute adrenal washout  
Relative adrenal washout  
Lung cancer TNM staging  
Tumour volume doubling time  
BTS nodule follow up guidelines - algorithm 2  
Fleischner Society nodule follow up guidelines 
Brock lung cancer risk 
Herder lung cancer risk
RECIST 1.1  
Colorectal cancer TNM staging  
Pancreatic cancer TNM staging  
Pancreatitis CT severity index  
Renal cancer TNM staging  
Bosniak classification of renal cystic lesions  
Endometrial cancer TNM staging  
Cervical cancer TNM staging  
Ovarian cancer TNM staging  
Prostate volume calculator  
Bladder volume calculator  
Estimated bladder capacity  
CT dose calculator
